{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892020/extras/Barbarization_GIF_616x166_009_FRAME.gif?t=1738269595\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892020/extras/Survive_Enemy_Hordes.png?t=1738269595\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Defeat enemies in each room to unlock your next reward. Survive longer for better rewards  or escape through the next open door if you have to.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892020/extras/Barbarization_GIF_616x166_007_FRAME.gif?t=1738269595\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892020/extras/Multiple_Upgrade_Systems.png?t=1738269595\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect ability cards, weapons, and trinkets to build a unique character each run. Experiment with different combinations of abilities, buffs and stat upgrades to find powerful synergies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892020/extras/Barbarization_GIF_616x166_002_C_FRAME.gif?t=1738269595\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892020/extras/Spectial_Events.png?t=1738269595\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete elite encounters, quests and world events to obtain unique rewards. Choose between story driven challenges and randomized adventures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2892020/extras/Barbarization_GIF_616x166_004_FRAME.gif?t=1738269595\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"